  Chhin-chhiuN7 teng2-pang Se-iuN5 toa7 sio-thai5 e5 tiong-kan, lan2 chit-peng5 chit8-si5 put-chi2 ho2 keng2-khi3. M7-ku2 sio-thai5 liau2-au7 put-ti put-kak e5 tiong-kan, chiN5-kui7 lai7 e5 chiN5-gun5, bo5 siaN bo5 soeh kan-ta poe bo5-khi3, teng2-jit8 put-chi2 iu-nga2 chheng-eng5 e5 lang5, kin-na2-jit8 tioh8 hou7 lang5 tah8-mng5 tah8-hou7. Ui7-tioh8 an2-ni khi2-siau2 iah-si7 chu7-chin7 e5 lang5 si7 be7-chio2, tui3 an2-ni lai5 choe3 cha3-khi hai7-lang5 e5 tai7-chi3, he si7 choe7-choe7 bo5-thang khi3 sng3-khi2. U7 chit8-e5 chhut-mia5 e5 thek-hak8-ka kio3-choe3 Bacon, u7 kong2 ¡§ho2-giah8-lang5 teh siuN7-chiN5 e5 si5, i si7 bo5-eng5 thang kou3 i e5 sin-the2 kap sim-koaN.¡¨ Sit8-chai7 si7 kong2-liau2 chin-chiaN3 tioh8. Bo5 tek-heng7, bo5 siu-iong2 e5 lang5 lai5 ho2-giah8, si7 bo5 koh-iuN7 piN7-lang5 teh gia5-ke5; cheng-chha phou2-thong e5 ke5 si7 chha5 choe3 e5, ho2-giah8-lang5 e5 ke5 si7 kim e5. Chong2-si7 ki3-jian5 kah si7 ke5, chha5 e5 kaN2 m7-si7 tian-to3 khah khiong-hi2, in-ui7 kim e5 khah tang7, si7 ju2 khah kho2-lin5. 
  3. ChaiN2-iuN7 chiah sng3-si7 ho2-giah8
  Ho2-giah8 chaiN2-iuN7 kong2 si7 m7-ho2? Teng2-chat sou2 kong2 ho2-giah8 bo5 tek-khak ho2, si7 kong2 gia5 chiN5-ke5 e5 ho2-giah8-lang5, bo5 chai5-cheng5 bo5 tek-heng7 e5 ho2-giah8 m7-ho2, m7-si7 kong2 kiN3-na7 ho2-giah8 chiu7 m7-ho2, tak8-lang5 tek-khak tioh8 long2 choe3 san3-sian chiah oe7 eng7-tit. M7-bian2 kong2 pat8-lang5; na7-si7 chin-chiaN3 e5 ho2-giah8, goa2 si7 hui-siong5 ai3. chong2-si7 na7 m7-si7 chin-chiaN3 e5, m7-bian2 kong2 si7 Khong2-chu2 kong2, chiu7-si7 goa2 ia7-si7 khoaN3-choe3 pi2 thiN-teng2 teh poe e5 hun5-bu7 iau2-ku2 khah bo5 hian7. Na7-si7 an2-ni, chaiN2-iuN7 chiah sng3 si7 chin-chiaN3 e5 ho2-giah8, che tioh8 lai5 gian2-kiu3 hou7 i beng5. 
  Te7-it tioh8-ai3 beng5-pek8, siu choe7, eng7 choe7 chiah si7 chin e5 ho2-giah8, kan-ta toa7-kui7 lai7 pa2-pa2, thou5-kha tai5 kui2-na7 chap8 ang3, thou2-te7 u7 kui2-chheng kui2-ban7 kah, chiN5-gun5 kan-ta pang3 teh hou7 i siN-sian, chhan5-hng5 si7 pai5 teh choe3 the2-bin7, iah si7 pang3 hou7 kiaN2-sun khi3 khui-sai2 khuiN3-oah8, che m7-si7 ho2-giah8, si7 kap sin-khu tng7 poaN3-iN5 e5 lang5 it-iuN7. 
  Lan2 siong5-siong5 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 chit-khoan2 lang5, li2 na7 sng3 i sou2-u7 e5 kim-gun5 si7 u7 kui2-chap8 ban7, chha5 i e5 chhan5-hng5 si7 u7 kui2-pah kah, lun7 i kap lang5 kau-koan iu7-si7 chin khoah-toa7. M7-ku2 kiN3-tioh8 kong-kiong7, ui7-tioh8 sia7-hoe7 u7 li7-ek e5 tai7-chi3, beh kio3 i ban2 chit8-ki khou2-mou-a2 chhut-lai5 hian3, i chiu7 hau2-kio3-thang3. Tui3 lang5 put-si5 hau2-kio3 i san3-hiong kan-khou2. Koh-chai3 chiu7-si7 i ka-ki7 mui2-jit8 e5 chiah8-chheng7-eng7, ia7-si7 kiu5 kap phou2-thong i2-ha7 e5 lang5 sio-siang7-khoan2, phau2-lou7 si7 eng7 kha, che7-chhia si7 hiam5 bo5 si3-teng2 e5. Chong2 kong2, na7 lun7 theh8-chhut, i si7 kiu5 choe3 bo5 lou7-eng7 e5 lang5; iah na7 tu2-tioh8 u7 thang theh8-jip8, i chiu7 phin2-sin phin2-se3 eng7 khah toa7 e5 pun2-chiN5 to si7 kaN2. Chit-cheng2 lang5 hian7-si5 chai7 lan2 e5 tiong-kan m7-chai u7 joa7 choe7? Chit-cheng2 chiu7-si7 chiaN3-pan7 e5 chiu2-chiN5-lou5, be7-eng7-tit sng3-si7 ho2-giah8. 
  Chin-chiaN3 e5 ho2-giah8-lang5 tioh8 oe7 choe7-jip8 choe7-chhut, leng5 chip8 leng5 soaN3 chiah si7. Goan5-lai5 chiN5-chai5 si7 beh hou7 lang5 eng7, hou7 lang5 choe3 tai7-chi3 e5 khi3-ku7, toan3-toan3 m7-si7 beh hou7 lang5 pai5 teh khoaN3 hong. ChiN5-gun5 tioh8 ju2 gau5 liu5-thong chiah ju2 u7 ke3-tat8, na7-si7 kan-ta tun3-si2 ti7 chit8-tah, choan kui ti7 chit8-e5 lang5 e5 chhiu2, si7 kap tun3 pun3-so3 kang7 it-iuN7. Koan-he7 chiN5-chai5 u7 nng7-chiong2 e5 koan5-li7, chit8-chiong2 si7 sou2-iu2-koan5, koh chit8-chiong2 si7 su2-iong7-koan5. SiaN2-hoe3 kio3-choe3 sou2-iu2-koan5? Lan2 mai3 tit theh8 hoat-lut8 e5 kong2-hoat lai5 kong2, chiau3 phou2-thong e5 li2-khi3 lai5 lun7. Phi2-lun7 ti7-chia u7 chit8-pah gun5. Chit pah-gun5 tek-khak m7-si7 ka-ki7 u7, tek-khak u7 chu2-lang5. Tui3 chit-e5 lang5 kong2, hit pah-gun5 si7 koa3 hit-e5 lang5 e5 mia5, pat8-lang5 na7 m7-si7 u7 theh8 kap hit pah-gun5 siang7 ke3-tat8 e5 mih8, kap chit-e5 lang5 hoaN-hi2 kam-goan7 sio tui3-oaN7, tek-khak be7 thang kai2-oaN7 hit pah-gun5 e5 mia5-ji7. U7 hit pah-gun5 e5 mia5-ji7 e5 lang5, chiu7-si7 kong2 tui3 hit pah-gun5 u7 sou2-iu2-koan5. Iah sim2-mih8 kio3-choe3 su2-iong7-koan5? Oe7-thang chu7-iu5 theh8 hit pah-gun5 khi3 khai-eng7 e5 lang5, chiu7-si7 u7 hit pah-gun5 e5 su2-iong7-koan5. Chin-chiaN3 e5 ho2-giah8, tioh8 u7 chin toa7 e5 sou2-iu2-koan5 kap su2-iong7-koan5. 
  Chong2-si7 na7 oe7-thang ku2-ku2 u7 chin khoah-toa7 e5 su2-iong7-koan5, kan-ta an2-ni ia7 chiok-giah8 thang kong2 si7 ho2-giah8. Kiam2-chhai2 chit-khoan2 e5 ho2-giah8 si7 khah ta-sang, khah sit8-chai7. Goan5-lai5 u7-chiN5 u7-mih8 kaN2 m7-si7 beh eng7 mah? Sou2-i2 u7-chiN5 u7-mih8 na7-si7 be7 thang eng7, iah-si7 be7-hiau2 eng7, he u7 si7 kap bo5 sio-siang7. 
  Phi2-lun7 kong2, u7 chit8-e5 ho2-giah8-lang5 si2 khi3, i e5 kiaN2 se3-han3, i e5 chai5-san2 bian2 kong2 si7 beh pang3 hou7 i e5 kiaN2, sou2-i2 hiah-e5 chai5-san2 e5 sou2-iu2-koan5 si7 siok8-ti7 hit-e5 gin2-na2. M7-ku2, in-ui7 hit-e5 gin2-na2 se3-han3 be7-hiau2 sim2-mih8, sou2-i2 jip8 i e5 chek-peh iah-si7 chhin-chhe3 choe3 i e5 hou7-kam3-jin5, the3 gin2-na2 chiang2-li2 hiah-e5 chai5-san2. Tui3 an2-ni hit-e5 hou7-kam3-jin5 na7 si7 bo5 u7 m7 cheng3-keng e5 tai7-chi3, i oe7 thang the3 hit e5 gin2-na2 chu2-i3, chiong hiah-e5 chai5-san2 ka7 i un7-iong7 hou7 i choe3 chiong2-chiong2 e5 su7-giap8. Na7-si7 an2-ni hiah-e5 chai5-san2 e5 su2-iong7-koan5 thang kong2 si7 kui-ti7 hou7-kam3-jin5 e5 chhiu2-lai7, hit-e5 gin2-na2 si7 u7 chit8-e5 khang-mia5, sit8-chai7 si7 hou7-kam3-jin5 teh ho2-giah8. Siat-su2 hit-e5 gin2-na2 na7-si7 ku2-ku2 be7 toa7-han3, iah-si7 chiaN5-choe3 chit8-e5 put-tiong7-iong7 e5 lang5, hit-e5 hou7-kam3-jin5 kaN2 m7-si7 ku2-ku2 oe7-thang un7-iong7 hiah-e5 chai5-san2 mah? I kaN2 m7-si7 ku2-ku2 si7 ho2-giah8? 
  Tui3 chit-hang7 thui-siong2 khi2-lai5 chiu7 oe7 beng5-pek8, tioh8 u7 su2-iong7-koan5 chiah si7 ho2-giah8, kan-ta u7 sou2-iu2-koan5 si7 bo5 i3-gi7, put-ko3 na7-si7 u7 sou2-iu2-koan5 koh-chai3 u7 su2-iong7-koan5, an2-ni si7 hou7 hit-e5 su2-iong7-koan5 oe7-thang khah an-un2 khah ku2-tng5 na7-tiaN7. Sui si7 an2-ni kong2, chit-e5 sou2-iu2-koan5-jin5 na7 ju2 chin3-pou7 tek-khak oe7 ju2 bo5 ti3-tiong7. U7 chiN5 m7-kam eng7, iah-si7 be7-hiau2 eng7, kin2-kin2 oe7-hiau2 siuN7 jip8 bo5 siuN7 chhut, chit-cheng2 lang5 kiam2-chhai2 u7 sou2-iu2-koan5, chong2-si7 tek-khak m7-si7 u7 su2-iong7-koan5, che si7 kap san3-hiong-lang5 bo5 koh-iuN7. 
  Te7-ji7 tioh8-ai3 beng5-pek8, put-lun7 choe7 iah si7 chio2, tioh8-ai3 si5-si5 u7 seng-sit chiah sng3-si7 ho2-giah8; na7-si7 mui2-jit8 kan-ta long2 si7 khai-hui3 siau bo5-khi3, long2 bo5 teng5-sin siN chhut sim2-mih8 pat8-hang7, chit-khoan2 si7 long2 u7 kiam2-chio2 bo5 ke-thiN, che chiaN3-chiaN3 si7 san3-hiong. Tai7-ke chai, liau2-boe2-kiaN2 sui si7 i e5 chou2-kong pang3 u7 kui2-chheng-ban7 hou7 i, kiu3-keng3 i si7 san3-hiong-lang5. M7-na7 an2-ni, kau3-boe2 lian5 i e5 seng-khu siN3-mia7 to soah bo5 thang u7 i e5 hun7. Iah na7-si7 jit8-jit8 teh choe3-kang, bo5-lun7 si7 tui3 ka-ki7, hek8-si7 tui3 sia7-hoe7, tak8-jit8 u7 li7-ek, tak8-jit8 u7 chhut-sit, u7 khah ke-thiN choe, an2-ni hit-e5 lang5 sui si7 hian7-si5 bo5 tiok8, chong2-si7 tek-khak oe7-thang sng3-choe3 ho2-giah8. M7-na7 i ho2-giah8, sia7-hoe7 ui7-tioh8 chit-cheng2 lang5 oe7 tit8-tit8 chin3-pou7, tit8-tit8 hoat-tat8. Chit-cheng2 lang5 thang kong2 si7 se3-kan e5 kim-khong3, tui3 hia beh chhut chin choe7 kim hou7 se3-kan iah-si7 i e5 kiaN2-sun u7 iu5-ji7. 
  Na7 theh8 sio2-sio2 e5 lai5 kong2, chit8-e5 lang5 chit8-jit8 than3 saN-kak, ka-ki7 eng7 nng7-kak; chhun chit8-kak theh8 hou7 pat8-lang5, choe3 lang5 e5 li7-ek; iah koh u7 chit8-lang5, chit8-jit8 than3 saN-khou, jit8-jit8 ka-ki7 tioh8 si3-khou chiah u7-kau3, bo5-kau3 eng7 hit-khou gun5, i chiu7 iong7-sim khi3 khek pat8-lang5 e5 lai5 pou2. ChhiaN2 siuN7 chit nng7-lang5, toh chit8-lang5 khah ho2-giah8? 
  Na7 theh8 khah toa7 e5 lai5 kong2, chu7 kou2 i2-lai5 e5 toa7-gau5-lang5, thang kong2 in si7 toa7 ho2-giah8. In si7 khoaN3 thang3 thiN-kha-e7 choe3 in e5 chhu3, in thang3-sin e5 lat8 long2 si7 chhut ti7 cheng3-lang5 e5 tiong-kan, hou7 cheng3-lang5 ui7-tioh8 in lai5 hoat-tian2 chin3-pou7. 
  Khong2-chu2 sui-jian5 chai7 Tan5-kok chit8-si5 bat bo5 bi2-niu5 thang chiah8, chong2-si7 se3-kan tui3 i lai5 siN e5 chai5-san2 si7 bo5-tang3 sng3. Sek-khia ai3 se3-kan bo5 kan-khou2, Sui-jian5 si7 chiong i e5 ong5-kiong, ong5-ui7 tan3 hiat-kak8, chong2-si7 au7-lai5 i sou2-tit e5 m7-chai pi2 hiah-e5 ke u7 kui2-chheng kui2-ban7 poe7? Ki-tok ka-ki7 u7 kong2: ¡§Ti7 thiN teh poe e5 chiau2-a2 u7 siu7 thang khun3, chai7 khong3-ia2 teh chau2 e5 hou5-li5 ia7-u7 khang thang bih, chong2-si7 goa2 si7 bo5 khoa3 thau5-khak e5 lang5.¡¨ Li2 khoaN3 hit-si5 i si7 ho5-teng2 e5 san3-hiong. TaN chhiaN2 khoaN3, hian7-si5 thong se3-kai3 chiaN5-poaN3 e5 lang5 kaN2 m7-si7 ui7-tioh8 i teh chhut-lat8? I thang kong2 si7 chu7 u7 lang5 i2-lai5 choe3 thau5-it-teng2 e5 ho2-giah8, put-lun7 to2 chit8-si5-tai7 e5 hong5-te3 ia7 be7 thang tat8-tit i e5 chit8-kak-a2! 
  Te7-saN ai3 chheng-chhou2 e5 tiam2, ho2-giah8 m7-si7 kong2 sou2-u7 e5 chiN5 tioh8-ai3 kau3 joa7 choe7? Si7 tioh8 oe7-hiau2 chai-iaN2 ka-ki7 e5 khui3-lat8, chiah lai5 siuN7 lan2 sou2 oe7 kham-tit e5 giah8-sou3, koh-chai3 tioh8 eng7 choe3 ho2 e5 hoat-tou7 lai5 un7-iong7 hiah-e5. na7-si7 an2-ni, chiu7 thang sng3-choe3 si7 ho2-giah8. 
  An2-ni kiam2-chhai2 kong2-liau2 khah hoan3, chhiaN2 lai5 thiah khah beng5. ChiN5 si7 chai5-cheng5 e5 phiau-ki3, che lan2 i2-keng u7 kong2-liau2. Lang5 e5 sim tui3 chiN5 lau2-sit8 si7 bo5 siuN7 ia3, m7-ku2 chiN5-chai5 ki3-jian5 kah-si7 chai5-cheng5 e5 phiau-ki3, tioh8-ai3 liong7 khui3-lat8 chiah tiaN7-tioh8 sou2 eng-kai tit e5 chiah si7. Na7 beh m7-si7 an2-ni, siat-su2 chiu7-si7 hou7 i ke tit khah choe7, i ia7-si7 un7-iong7 be7 thang khi3, an2-ni m7-na7 hiah-e5 chin5 chek si2-si2, i e5 taN3 ia7-si7 ke tang7, tioh8 siu7 chiong2-chiong2 e5 chou2-gai7. 
  Phi2-ju7 chit8-e5 lang5 beh siu-tang, kio3 i e5 kiaN2-ji5 long2-chong2 chhut-mng5 tau3 koah-tiu7. Koah liau2, si7-toa7-lang5 khoaN3 in long2 kut-lat8, put-chi2 toa7 hoaN-hi2, un2-chun2 in hiaN-ti7 kok-lang5 chin7 in sou2-u7 e5 khui3-lat8 taN tiu7 khi3 choe3 sai-khia. Toa7-han3 e5 taN chit8-pah kin; te7 ji7 e5 taN peh-chap8 kin; long2 tu2-a2-ho2, oe7-thang taN kau3 chhu3. Te7 saN e5, se3-han3 m7 jin7-hun7, i siuN7 chit8-si5-a2 ku2 e5 kan-khou2 na7-tiaN7, khah choe7 oe7-thang khai-sai2 khah khuiN3-oah8, sou2-i2 i chiu7 kiong7-kiong7 chng kap in toa7-ko taN sio-siang7, taN chit8-pou7, tian nng7-pou7, taN kau3 toa7-khui3 chhoan2 be7 li7. Bo5 ta5-oa5 tioh8-ai3 piaN3 chit8-toa7-poaN3 ti7 lou7-piN hou7 cheng-siN chiah8, iah i ka-ki7 kau3 chhu3 soah hoat-jiat8 thau5-thiaN3, lian5 to2 kui2-na7 jit8. I e5 lau7-pe7 chhio3-chhio3, ka7 i kong2: ¡§Gong7 gin2-na2, li2 m7-tioh8 chun2-chat ka-ki7 e5 khui3-lat8. Na7 beh chhin-chhiuN7 li2 an2-ni, goa2 hit-chun7 tioh8 m7-thang hou7 li2, chiah be7 hai7 li2.¡¨ Lan2 kong2 ¡§tham-ji7 phin5-ji7 khak¡¨, Se-iuN5 ia7-si7 an2-ni kong2 ¡§lang5 m7-si7 in-ui7 i sou2-u7 e5 mih8 khah chio2, sou2-i2 chiah san3-hiong; tok8-tok8 si7 in-ui7 i e5 sim m7-chai chiok chiah si7.¡¨ 
  ChiN5-gun5 tioh8 khoaN3 eng7 e5 hoat-tou7, kap eng7 e5 sou2-chai7, na7-si7 eng7-tioh8 e5 hoat-tou7 kap eng7 ti7 tioh8 e5 sou2-chai7, chit8-e5 chiN5 oe7 chiaN5-choe3 nng7-e5 iah-si7 saN, si3 e5 chiN5 kau7. Iah na7-si7 eng7 m7-ho2 e5 hoat-tou7, lai5 eng7 ti7 m7-tioh8 e5 sou2-chai7, sui-jian5 si7 chiN5-gun5 chek kau3 moa2-chhu3 lai7, che toan3-toan3 be7-eng7-tit kong2 si7 ho2-giah8, bo5 koh-iuN7 si7 chek kui keng e5 pun3-so3. 
  Bi2-kok u7 chit8-e5 toa7 chhut-mia5-lang5 kio3-choe3 Franklin. I kong2: ¡§Lang5 kiaN5 chit8-pai2 phaiN2 phin2-heng7 e5 hui3-iong7, oe7-thang iong2-iok8 nng7-e5 gin2-na2.¡¨ Chong2-si7 goa2 siuN7 kaN2 put-chi2 si7 an2-ni. Chiau3 goa2 e5 keng-giam7 kong2, khai ti7 kong-nih chit8-e5 chiN5, m7-na7 khai ti7 su-nih pah-e5 chiN5 e5 kau7. ChhiaN2 khoaN3, piaN3 siN3-mia7 ui7-tioh8 chit8-ke e5 bou2-kiaN2 chhut-lat8, chiong it-chhe3 sou2-u7 e5 kan-ta ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 lai5 khai-hui3, keng3-jian5 kau3-boe2 piN3-choe3 kui2-te3 bo5-mia5 bo5 seN3 e5 kut-thau5; chit-khoan2 lang5 m7-chai i2-keng u7 joa7 choe7. M7-bian2 kong2 pat8-lang5, lan2 ka-ki7 lai5 choe3 khoaN3, chiong lan2 ai3 kou3 bou2-kiaN2 e5 chiN5-chai5 khui3-lat8, pun chit8-koa2-a2 tui3 sia7-hoe7 cheng3-lang5 choe3 khoaN3 leh, li2 tek-khak oe7 kam2-kak li2 sou2-eng7 e5 chit8-iN5 u7 pah-iN5 toa7. U7 chit8-ban7 ke-si e5 lang5, tek-khak oe7-thang piN3-choe3 pah-ban7 e5 tiong2-chia2. 
  Liat8-ui7, m7-thang kong2 goa2 si7 teh kong2 hong-tong5, che si7 tui3 goa2 ka-ki7 e5 keng-giam7, kap khoaN3 se3-kan e5 sit8-cheng5, eng7 khah chhiat e5 sin3-liam7 ti7-teh kong2. Liat8-ui7, chhiaN2 boh8-gi5, seng5-sim khi3 choe3 khoaN3, goa2 sin3 liat8-ui7 ia7 tek-khak oe7 toa7-siaN hoah kong2: ¡§Tioh8!¡¨ Kou2-cha2 Iu5-thai3 I2-sek-liat8 kok e5 ong5 Sou2-lo5-mng5 u7 kong2: ¡§U7 sia2-si, hoan2-tng2 ke-thiN ho2-giah8; u7 po2-sioh chiN5, hoan2-tng2 san3-hiong.¡¨ Sit8-chai7 si7 chian-kou2 e5 kim-gian5. 
  4. Si5-khek si7 ng5-kim 
  ¡§Chian-ka-si¡¨ e5 thau5-cham7 u7 chit8-ku3 kong2: ¡§Chhun-thiN e5 am3-si5 chit8-khek-a2 ku2 oe7-thang tat8-tit chit8 chheng-kim.¡¨ Chit-ku3-si si7 kek8-lek8 teh o-lo2 chhun-thiN geh-kng si5 e5 ho2 keng2-ti3, si7 kong2 khoaN3 hit-khoan2 e5 ho2 keng2-ti3 chit8-tiap8-a2-ku2, si7 pi2 tit-tioh8 chit8-chheng kim khah ho2. Che si7 tui3 keng2-ti3 lai5 bat si5-khek e5 kui3-tiong7. Na7 bo5 u7 keng2-ti3 hiah ho2, phah-sng3 i kaN2 be7-hiau2 tit hit-sut-a2 ku2 e5 si5-khek u7 kah hiah po2-poe3. Sui-jian5 si7 an2-ni kong2, che ia7 iau2-ku2 oe7-thang kong2 si7 bat si5-khek e5 ke3-tat8 e5 lang5. 
  ¡§Si5-khek si7 ng5-kim¡¨ (Time is money) chit-ku3 oe7 si7 Se-iuN5 e5 siok8-gi2. Lan2 tui3 chit-ku3 oe7 thang chai Se-iuN5-lang5 bat si5-khek e5 kui3-tiong7, si7 pi2 lan2 u7 khah chhim, khah kau3-thau5. Chit-ku3 oe7 e5 i3-su3 si7 khoaN3-tioh8 si5-khek chiu7 chai-iaN2 si5-khek e5 kui3-tiong7, si7 kong2-tioh8 ho2 keng2-ti3 e5 si5 chiah si7. 
  Tui3 ho2 keng2-ti3 chiah oe7-hiau2 si5-khek si7 tat8-chiN5 e5, kiam2-chhai2 tu2-tioh8 phaiN2 keng2-ti3, phaiN2 keng2-hong2 e5 si5, beh kong2 si5-khek pi2 noa7-thou5 khah thang iam3-ok, ia7 ku2-kaN2. KhoaN3-tioh8 si5-khek chiu7 chai si5-khek si7 kui3-tiong7 e5 lang5, put-lun7 si7 ho2 keng2-ti3 iah-si7 phaiN2 keng2-gu7, ho2-giah8-lang5 e5 chit8 tiam2-cheng kap san3-hiong-lang5 e5 chit8 tiam2-cheng, i to long2 si7 khoaN3-choe3 chin tat8-chiN5, peN5-peN5 si7 kui3-tiong7. In-ui7 an2-ni, Se-iuN5-lang5 si7 chin gau5 po2-sioh si5-khek, chit8-tiap8-a2-ku2 to bo5 pang3 hou7 i khang-khang chau2 koe3-khi3. 
  Lan2 e5 lang5 si7 chin be7-hiau2 si5-khek e5 tat8-chiN5, khoaN3 si5-khek na2 chhin-chhiuN7 teh khoaN3 toa7-khe e5 chui2, pang3 ku3-chai7 i tit8-tit8 lau5 koe3-khi3. In kap lan2 chu7 chin ku2 e5 i2-cheng5, koh-chai3 si7 chin choe7 lang5, tui3 si5-khek u7 chit-khoan2 koh-iuN7 e5 khoaN3-hoat, ti3-kau3 chai7 kin-na2-jit8, in e5 bun5-beng5 kap lan2 e5 si7 toa7-toa7 u7 koh-iuN7. In teh koe3-jit8 e5 chu-bi7 si7 kap lan2 toa7-toa7 bo5 sio-siang7. M7-bian2 kong2 Se-iuN5-lang5 si7 pi2 lan2 khah oe7-hiau2 khui kim-soaN, gau5 hoat-beng5, gau5 che3-cho7 ki5-khiau2 e5 mih8-kiaN7. Kin2-kin2 tui3 chit-tiam2 pi2 lan2 khah gau5 po2-tiong7 si5-khek e5 sim-seng3 lai5 kong2, chiu7-si7 i2-keng pi2 lan2 chin hu3-ju7 chin ho2-giah8, chin khoai3-lok8, chin u7 i3-gi7 lah. Thang kong2 in e5 chit8-jit8 kiam2-chhai2 beh khah iaN5 lan2 e5 chit8-ni5. 
  Si5-khek hou7 lang5 thang kui3-tiong7 e5 li2-iu5 u7 nng7-hang7. Chit8-hang7 si7 in-ui7 si5-khek chit8-e7 koe3-khi3, chiu7 bo5 koh to3-tng2-lai5. Lan2 m7-thang kong2 chah8-cha2 khi2, iau2-ku2 u7 kim-cha2-khi2; kim-cha2-khi2 koe3 liau2, iau2-ku2 u7 bin5-a2-chai3 cha2-khi2 thang lai5. Sui-jian5 peN5-peN5 si7 cha2-khi2, chong2-si7 chah8-cha2-khi2 kap kim-cha2-khi2 si7 bo5-siang7; kim-cha2-khi2 kap bin5-a2 cha2-khi2 ia7-si7 u7 cheng-chha. Chu7 kou2-cha2 e5 kou2-cha2, kau3 au7-lai5 e5 au7-lai5, kim cha2-khi2 kin2-kin2 chiah u7 chit8-e5, kaN2 m7-si7 chin thang kui3-tiong7 mah! 
  Koh chit8-hang7 si7 in-ui7 si5-khek kap lang5 e5 oah8-mia7 be7 lan5-tit, oe7-thang kong2 si5-khek chiu7-si7 lang5 e5 siN3-mia7. Si5-khek e5 keng-koe3 ko2-jian5 si7 bo5-han7-liong7, m7-ku2 chai7 chit-e5 bo5-han7-liong7 e5 si5-khek e5 lai7-bin7, lan2 oe7-thang oah8-tong7, phou2-thong chiah kin2-kin2 u7 gou7-chap8 ni5-ku2. Chit gou7-chap8 ni5 e5 tiong-kan, oe7-thang choe3-kang, pan7 tai7-chi3 e5 si5-jit8 si7 bo5 joa7 choe7. Gou7-chap8 ni5 e5 tiong-kan tioh8 khun3 liau2 chap8-lak, chhit ni5. Thak8-chheh chun2-pi7 e5 si5-kan chun2 choe3 lak8-ni5 ku2, se3-han3 be7-hiau2 poaN3-hang7, be7 thang chhong3 sim2-mih8; kap lang5 ia3-sian7 iah si7 phoa3-piN7 chong2-kiong7 chun2-choe3 chap8-ni5 ku2. It-chhe3 khau3-tu5 goa7, gou7-chap8 ni5 e5 tiong-kan oe7-thang hoat-hui lang5 e5 khui3-lat8 choe3 tai7-chi3, kan-ta chiah u7 chap8-lak8 iah si7 chap8-chhit ni5 ku2. Thang chai chit8-si3-lang5 e5 tiong-kan oah8-liau2 choe3 u7 khoan2-sit, choe3 u7 i3-gi7 e5 si5-jit8, Put-ko3 m7 chiuN7 ji7-chap8 ni5. Chit chap8-lak8, chhit ni5 na7 pang3 hou7 i khang-khang lau5 koe3-khi3, lang5 u7 oah8 si7 kap bo5 sio-siang7, hit-e5 lang5 si7 kap bo5 siN3-mia7 e5 lang5 it-iuN7. 
  Li2 siuN7 khoaN3, si5-khek tioh8-ai3 po2-sioh iah m7-bian2? Si5-khek sit8-chai7 si7 ng5-kim, m7-na7 an2-ni, iau2-ku2 si7 pi2 ng5-kim koh-chai3 khah kui3-khi3. Lan2 hiaN-ti7 chi2-be7 e5 tiong-kan, m7-chai si7 in-ui7 chaiN2-iuN7, kan-ta oe7-hiau2 kui3-tiong7 chiN5-gun5 kap siN3-mia7, iah khoaN3 si5-khek chhin-chhiuN7 thou5, hit-ho7 lang5 chin choe7. 
  ChhiaN2 jin7-chin siuN7 khoaN3, kiu3-keng3 chiN5-gun5 kap siN3-mia7 to long2 si7 si5-khek lai5 hou7 i chiaN5 e5. Kan-ta oe7-hiau2 tiong7 chiN5 ai3 siN3-mia7, be7-hiau2 po2-sioh si5-khek, che si7 bo5 koh-iuN7 chiah8 koe2-chi2 be7-hiau2 kou3 chhiu7-chang5; tiong7 chiong7-goan5 soah bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 ka-ki7 e5 sian-siN. Goa2 ti7-chai beh ki2 kui2-chan5 lai5 choe3 cheng3-ku3. ChhiaN2 tai7-ke choe3-hoe2 chim-chiok khoaN3. 
  Tak8-jit8 tui3 ke-lou7 koe3, put-si5 to u7 khoaN3-kiN3 lan2 teh be2-be7 si7 chin-chiaN3 gau5 kong2-ke3. Be7 e5 lang5 chai-iaN2 be2 e5 lang5 tek-khak oe7 chhut-ke3, i chiu7 chiong ke3-chiN5 kong2 hou7 i phang3-be2 phang3-be2, ku3-chai7 i khi3 chhut. Be2 e5 lang5 iau2-be7 khoaN3 mih8-kiaN7 e5 ho2-bai2, khui-chhui3 chiu7 hiam5 khah kui3. ¡§Tng5-soaN kheh, tui3-poaN3 soeh¡¨, chiu7 seng ka7 i chhut chit8-e7 hou7 i siok8-siok8-siok8, iah chiah na2 khoaN3 mih8 na2 chhui-chhiau5. 
  Tai7-ke siuN7 chin khoaN3, sou2 chhui-chhek8 e5 ke3-siau3 cheng-chha u7 joa7 choe7? Che si7 khoai3 chai-iaN2, chong2-si7 ui7-tioh8 an2-ni sou2 liau2 e5 si5-khek, sui-jian5 si7 gou7-hun, chap8-hun e5 ku2, chit gou7 hun-cheng, chap8 hun-cheng e5 ke3-chiN5, sit8-chai7 chin lan5-tit sng3, chit gou7 hun-cheng ku2, chiu7-si7 liau2-khi3 be2 e5 lang5 gou7-hun e5 siN3-mia7. Ui7-tioh8 kui2-chiam kui2-kak e5 kong2-ke3 kam-goan7 chhek liau2 gou7 hun, chap8-hun e5 hoe3-siu7, lau2-sit8 bo5 pi2 che khah gong7 e5! 
  Chit-khoan2 e5 be2-mih8 tui3 toh8-loh8 u7 thang siok8, chit-khoan2 e5 be7-mih8 chaiN2-iuN7 u7 thang than3? Hian7-kim kiam2-chhai2 u7 thang ke tiong5 kui2-kak gun5, chong2-si7 put-ti put-kak e5 tiong-kan i2-keng chhek liau2 kui2 hun e5 siN3-mia7. Ui7-tioh8 chiah chio2 e5 chiN5-gun5, kheng2 pang3 kui2-hun e5 siN3-mia7, chit-khoan2 e5 siN3-mia7 be7-bian2 siuN koe3 siok8. KiN3 chin chit8-hun e5 siN3-mia7 na7 eng7 kui2 chheng-ban7 gian5 beh ka7 lang5 be2, phah-sng3 i kaN2 m7. Tui3 si5-kan e5 koan-liam7 bo5-beng5, be7-hiau2-tit si5-khek e5 po2-poe3, sou2-i2 siong5-siong5 u7 chit-khoan2 gong7 e5 tai7-chi3, tak8-jit8 u7 hui-siong5 e5 sun2-hai7, bo5 li7-ek. 
  Bun5-beng5-lang5 kek8 gau5 ti3-tiong7 si5-khek; in e5 lang5 be2-be7 tek-khak bo5 an2-ni, be7 e5 lang5 chiau3 i sou2 oe7 hah8-poaN5 e5 ke3 kong2, be2 e5 lang5 ia7 chiau3 i sou2 khoaN3 oe7 tat8-tit ka7 i be2. Na7-si7 khoaN3 be7 hah8, i hoan-sin oat-tng2 chiu7 kiaN5, tai7-ke chin chheng-chhou2, chin bo5 hui3-khi3, chin seng2-kang. 
