  Se-iuN5-lang5 teh chiu2 si5-khek si7 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 teh kou3 siN3-mia7; kap lang5 iok an2-ni, chiu7-si7 an2-ni, iok kui2-tiam2 kui2 hun kau3, chiu7-si7 chiau3 hit-e5 si5-khek, tek-khak bo5 chha poaN3-hun. Tek-kok u7 chit8-e5 toa7 chhut-mia5-lang5 kio3-choe3 Kant, i m7 han7-teng7 tui3 pat8-lang5 choat8-tui3 si5-kan, chiu7-si7 i ka-ki7 to long2 si7 chiau3 si5-kan teh tin2-tang7 choe3 tai7-chi3. I tak8-jit8 to long2 u7 chit8-e5 tiaN7-tioh8 e5 si5-khek tioh8 chhut-khi3 goa7-bin7 kiaN5-soa2. In-ui7 i long2 u7 chiau3 si5-chun7, sou2-i2 lang5 na7 khoaN3-kiN3 i tui3 chit8 sou2-chai7 keng-koe3, chiu7 chai-iaN2 hit-chun7 si7 kui2 tiam2-cheng. Chai7 Se-iuN5 si7 liah8 bo5 chiu2 si5-kan e5 sou2 kiaN5 choe3 chit8-hang7 chin toa7 e5 phaiN2 heng5-ui5. 
